                    <span>The book is about a boy that is a boy on the beach with a woman that said that was his mother he did not believe him a the towin bully he killed on accident with some unknown power. He lost his sight.  He and went to a unknown island and met a frend bird.  He called him trouble and met a girl in the woods and they became friends and went to a castle to save the land.
